# Azure Lab Architecture

## Overview

This lab demonstrates a repeatable Azure administration workflow using PowerShell to deploy, inventory, and clean up Azure resources.

## Architecture Diagram

```text
+----------------------+
| Administrator        |
| (PowerShell 7)       |
+----------+-----------+
           |
           v
+----------------------+
| Connect-AzAccount    |
+----------+-----------+
           |
           v
+----------------------+
| Azure Subscription   |
+----------+-----------+
           |
           v
+----------------------+
| Resource Group       |
+----------+-----------+
           |
           v
+----------------------+
| Azure Resources      |
| - Storage            |
| - Networking         |
| - Virtual Machines   |
+----------+-----------+
           |
           v
+----------------------+
| Reporting Scripts    |
+----------+-----------+
           |
           v
+----------------------+
| Cleanup Script       |
+----------------------+
```

## Workflow

1. Authenticate with Azure.
2. Create or use a Resource Group.
3. Deploy or inventory Azure resources.
4. Generate reports.
5. Remove lab resources after testing.

